									<p class="elementor-icon-box-description">
						Using Pump automatically Transfer the pre-mixed deodorant material to the filling machine’s hopper. For thick stick deodorant pastes, start the hopper’s gentle stirring and heating system to maintain homogeneity and prevent ingredient segregation; for low-viscosity roll-on or spray liquids, skip stirring but ensure the material is free of impurities.					</p>
				
