							1.Filling						</span>
					</h3>
				
									<p class="elementor-icon-box-description">
						The machine dispenses the exact amount of hot melt liquid into each mold cavity. The molds are usually placed on a temperature-controlled plate to manage the cooling rate. Dosing system is adapt volumetric piston.					</p>
				
			</div>
			
